{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/posts/2fluV8sa5","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"ac06c06e-8461-5713-8e6a-ac8f739c3f00","excerpt":"記事一覧 その1（調査編） その2（USB編） その3（Nucleo編） その4（ケーブル編）　←ココ その5（最終章） 接続ケーブル作成 PS1とArduinoで接続するためにはケーブルが必要なので、中古でPS…","html":"<p>記事一覧</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/posts/mmx5El0Si\">その1（調査編）</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/posts/2stNWIQ7Z\">その2（USB編）</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/posts/vORCOiXb_\">その3（Nucleo編）</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/posts/2fluV8sa5\">その4（ケーブル編）</a>　←ココ</li>\n<li><a href=\"/posts/kuG0eT691\">その5（最終章）</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"接続ケーブル作成\" style=\"position:relative;\">接続ケーブル作成</h1>\n<p>PS1とArduinoで接続するためにはケーブルが必要なので、中古でPS1コントローラーを買って、そいつからケーブルだけ拝借することにした。単純に考えればケーブルをちょん切るだけでいいのだけど、それでは面白くないのでひと手間かけてみた。</p>\n<p>まずはコイツを\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f0d10ffe8d67e688e4854dd16f85a3e5/212bf/pic01.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.08108108108109%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"pic01\"\n        title=\"pic01\"\n        src=\"/static/f0d10ffe8d67e688e4854dd16f85a3e5/1c72d/pic01.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f0d10ffe8d67e688e4854dd16f85a3e5/a80bd/pic01.jpg 148w,\n/static/f0d10ffe8d67e688e4854dd16f85a3e5/1c91a/pic01.jpg 295w,\n/static/f0d10ffe8d67e688e4854dd16f85a3e5/1c72d/pic01.jpg 590w,\n/static/f0d10ffe8d67e688e4854dd16f85a3e5/212bf/pic01.jpg 768w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<br>\n<p>分解\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8987a7d2a7134ed7b93be9ab05bd2b85/212bf/pic02.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.08108108108109%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"pic02\"\n        title=\"pic02\"\n        src=\"/static/8987a7d2a7134ed7b93be9ab05bd2b85/1c72d/pic02.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8987a7d2a7134ed7b93be9ab05bd2b85/a80bd/pic02.jpg 148w,\n/static/8987a7d2a7134ed7b93be9ab05bd2b85/1c91a/pic02.jpg 295w,\n/static/8987a7d2a7134ed7b93be9ab05bd2b85/1c72d/pic02.jpg 590w,\n/static/8987a7d2a7134ed7b93be9ab05bd2b85/212bf/pic02.jpg 768w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<br>\n<p>ここで繋がっているので…\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 432px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/376782e264033c52fb8332f8b1a40333/08871/pic03.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 177.7027027027027%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"pic03\"\n        title=\"pic03\"\n        src=\"/static/376782e264033c52fb8332f8b1a40333/08871/pic03.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/376782e264033c52fb8332f8b1a40333/a80bd/pic03.jpg 148w,\n/static/376782e264033c52fb8332f8b1a40333/1c91a/pic03.jpg 295w,\n/static/376782e264033c52fb8332f8b1a40333/08871/pic03.jpg 432w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 432px) 100vw, 432px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<br>\n<p>ここのはんだを剥がす！\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 469px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/60b9ba858af32ab87a0c58f9bd1f5bc9/a76eb/pic04.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 60.810810810810814%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"pic04\"\n        title=\"pic04\"\n        src=\"/static/60b9ba858af32ab87a0c58f9bd1f5bc9/a76eb/pic04.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/60b9ba858af32ab87a0c58f9bd1f5bc9/a80bd/pic04.jpg 148w,\n/static/60b9ba858af32ab87a0c58f9bd1f5bc9/1c91a/pic04.jpg 295w,\n/static/60b9ba858af32ab87a0c58f9bd1f5bc9/a76eb/pic04.jpg 469w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 469px) 100vw, 469px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<br>\n<p>摘出完了！\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 365px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/bdcf1796df1554793e07e40c3128b2f2/60097/pic05.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 104.05405405405406%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"pic05\"\n        title=\"pic05\"\n        src=\"/static/bdcf1796df1554793e07e40c3128b2f2/60097/pic05.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/bdcf1796df1554793e07e40c3128b2f2/a80bd/pic05.jpg 148w,\n/static/bdcf1796df1554793e07e40c3128b2f2/1c91a/pic05.jpg 295w,\n/static/bdcf1796df1554793e07e40c3128b2f2/60097/pic05.jpg 365w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 365px) 100vw, 365px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<br>\n<p>ついでにコントローラーにピンソケットを付けてみる\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5b4ec7fc0f084adbff55b1a848c2a2b9/212bf/pic06.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.08108108108109%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"pic06\"\n        title=\"pic06\"\n        src=\"/static/5b4ec7fc0f084adbff55b1a848c2a2b9/1c72d/pic06.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5b4ec7fc0f084adbff55b1a848c2a2b9/a80bd/pic06.jpg 148w,\n/static/5b4ec7fc0f084adbff55b1a848c2a2b9/1c91a/pic06.jpg 295w,\n/static/5b4ec7fc0f084adbff55b1a848c2a2b9/1c72d/pic06.jpg 590w,\n/static/5b4ec7fc0f084adbff55b1a848c2a2b9/212bf/pic06.jpg 768w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<br>\n<p>これで元のコントローラーに戻すこともできる！！  </p>\n<p>各線はこんな感じになっている。\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2d61a66a95b05fcee1de13325f76bab8/561da/pic07.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 104.72972972972974%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"pic07\"\n        title=\"pic07\"\n        src=\"/static/2d61a66a95b05fcee1de13325f76bab8/fcda8/pic07.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2d61a66a95b05fcee1de13325f76bab8/12f09/pic07.png 148w,\n/static/2d61a66a95b05fcee1de13325f76bab8/e4a3f/pic07.png 295w,\n/static/2d61a66a95b05fcee1de13325f76bab8/fcda8/pic07.png 590w,\n/static/2d61a66a95b05fcee1de13325f76bab8/efc66/pic07.png 885w,\n/static/2d61a66a95b05fcee1de13325f76bab8/561da/pic07.png 969w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<br>\n<br>\nつづく。","frontmatter":{"title":"USB GamePad to PSX Controller Converter を作った(4)","date":"2019-02-17T22:45:21.000+09:00","description":"","tags":["製作記"]}}},